        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"I hate them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "The countess placed herself before Monte Cristo, still holding in her hand a portion of the perfumed grapes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Take some,\" she said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000037_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000037_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Madame, I never eat Muscatel grapes,\" replied Monte Cristo, as if the subject had not been mentioned before. The countess dashed the grapes into the nearest thicket, with a gesture of despair.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000037_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000037_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "Monte Cristo remained as unmoved as if the reproach had not been addressed to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000037_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000037_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "Albert at this moment ran in.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000037_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000037_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Oh, mother,\" he exclaimed, \"such a misfortune has happened!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"What?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "What has happened?\" asked the countess, as though awakening from a sleep to the realities of life; \"did you say a misfortune?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "Indeed, I should expect misfortunes.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Well?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Ah, indeed?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Albert, Albert,\" said Madame de Morcerf, in a tone of mild reproof, \"what are you saying?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "Ah, count, he esteems you so highly, tell him that he has spoken amiss.\" And she took two or three steps forward. Monte Cristo watched her with an air so thoughtful, and so full of affectionate admiration, that she turned back and grasped his hand; at the same time she seized that of her son, and joined them together.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"We are friends; are we not?\" she asked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Oh, madame, I do not presume to call myself your friend, but at all times I am your most respectful servant.\" The countess left with an indescribable pang in her heart, and before she had taken ten steps the count saw her raise her handkerchief to her eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"Do not my mother and you agree?\" asked Albert, astonished.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2929_86777_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2929/86777/2929_86777_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2929",
        "content": "\"On the contrary,\" replied the count, \"did you not hear her declare that we were friends?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
